Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.28,0:02:16.42,Default,,0,0,0,,No! An Angel! He was our enemy!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.44,0:02:17.65,Matisse Sign,,0,0,0,,EVEN THOUGH HE WAS HUMAN, LIKE YOU?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.65,0:02:20.72,Default,,0,0,0,,No! No! You're wrong!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.69,0:02:23.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Even though he was a person, just like me?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.78,0:02:26.31,Default,,0,0,0,,No! He was an Angel!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.31,0:02:27.95,Default,,0,0,0,,That's why you killed him?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.95,0:02:31.35,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right! If I hadn't, we would've died!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.35,0:02:33.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Everyone would have been killed!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.02,0:02:34.29,Default,,0,0,0,,That's why you killed him?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.29,0:02:36.16,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't do it because I wanted to!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.16,0:02:37.92,Default,,0,0,0,,I had no choice.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.97,0:02:38.97,Matisse Sign,,0,0,0,,THAT'S WHY YOU KILLED HIM
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.44,0:02:40.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Help me...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.47,0:02:41.47,Matisse Sign,,0,0,0,,THAT'S WHY YOU KILLED HIM
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.47,0:02:42.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Help me.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.68,0:02:43.60,Matisse Sign,,0,0,0,,THAT'S WHY YOU KILLED HIM
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.60,0:02:44.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Help me!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.60,0:02:46.14,Matisse Sign,,0,0,0,,THAT'S WHY YOU KILLED HIM
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.14,0:02:47.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Someone, help me!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.68,0:02:48.81,Matisse Sign,,0,0,0,,THAT'S WHY YOU KILLED HIM
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.58,0:02:51.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Please, someone just help me!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.28,0:03:00.52,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right, Kaworu was the one\Nwho should have survived.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.19,0:03:04.37,Default,,0,0,0,,He was a much better person than I am.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.93,0:03:07.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Kaworu should have been the one to survive.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.49,0:03:08.62,Default,,0,0,0,,You're wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.62,0:03:11.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Only those who have the will\Nto live get to survive.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.87,0:03:13.66,Default,,0,0,0,,He wished to die.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.66,0:03:16.94,Default,,0,0,0,,He abandoned his will to live,\Nclinging instead to a false hope.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.74,0:03:19.87,Default,,0,0,0,,You did nothing wrong, Shinji.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.87,0:03:21.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that true?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.09,0:03:21.80,Matisse Sign,,0,0,0,,UNCERTAINTY
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.80,0:03:24.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Is this really how it should be?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.05,0:03:24.55,Matisse Sign,,0,0,0,,HAUNTING UNCERTAINTY
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.55,0:03:27.74,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know. What should I do?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.74,0:03:29.13,Default,,0,0,0,,What am I supposed to do?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.14,0:03:30.18,Matisse Sign,,0,0,0,,WHAT ARE YOU AFRAID OF?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.18,0:03:31.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Afraid of?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.27,0:03:32.14,Matisse Sign,,0,0,0,,WHAT ARE YOU AFRAID OF?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.14,0:03:33.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Me?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.23,0:03:34.10,Matisse Sign,,0,0,0,,WHAT ARE YOU AFRAID OF?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.10,0:03:35.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Being hated.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.44,0:03:36.23,Matisse Sign,,0,0,0,,WHAT ARE YOU AFRAID OF?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.23,0:03:36.94,Default,,0,0,0,,By whom?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.98,0:03:37.57,Matisse Sign,,0,0,0,,WHAT ARE YOU AFRAID OF?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.30,0:03:38.56,Default,,0,0,0,,By whom?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.28,0:03:38.78,Matisse Sign,,0,0,0,,WHAT ARE YOU AFRAID OF?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.56,0:03:41.82,Default,,0,0,0,,By Father!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.82,0:03:44.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Father abandoned me! He hated me!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.74,0:03:47.83,Default,,0,0,0,,What will I do if people hate me?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.83,0:03:49.57,Default,,0,0,0,,What should I do?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.52,0:04:01.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Where am I?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.52,0:04:04.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Where am I supposed to go?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.82,0:04:07.86,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't see anything. I don't know what's what.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.70,0:04:11.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Miss Misato?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.63,0:04:14.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Miss Misato?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.63,0:04:17.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, where did you go, Miss Misato?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.47,0:04:22.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, where am I supposed to go now?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.81,0:04:26.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Miss Misato! Asuka! Ayanami!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.17,0:04:28.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Toji! Kensuke! Miss Ritsuko!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.57,0:04:30.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Kaji!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.00,0:04:31.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Father!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.82,0:04:33.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Mother...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.69,0:04:35.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Someone tell me.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.85,0:04:38.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Tell me what I'm supposed to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.59,0:04:42.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Evangelion Unit 01...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.06,0:04:48.43,Default,,0,0,0,,So, do I ultimately have no choice\Nbut to pilot it?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.97,0:04:51.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Even after killing someone I loved?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.36,0:04:54.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you saying I'm supposed to listen\Nto my father and everyone else,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.09,0:04:56.03,Default,,0,0,0,,and get back in this thing to fight?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.03,0:04:57.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Mother!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.46,0:04:59.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Say something! Answer me!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.69,0:05:00.90,Matisse Sign,,0,0,0,,WHY DO YOU PILOT THE EVA?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.35,0:05:04.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Because everyone tells me to pilot it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.15,0:05:05.40,Matisse Sign,,0,0,0,,THAT'S WHY YOU PILOT THE EVA?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.55,0:05:09.66,Default,,0,0,0,,It's... It's for the good of everybody,\Nso why does it matter?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.70,0:05:11.74,Matisse Sign,,0,0,0,,SO, YOU PILOT THE EVA FOR EVERYBODY,\NFOR OTHERS?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.74,0:05:14.59,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right. It's a good thing!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.59,0:05:16.75,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a very good thing!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.75,0:05:20.80,Default,,0,0,0,,If I pilot it, everyone praises me!\NThey treat me well!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.80,0:05:22.46,Default,,0,0,0,,That's a lie!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.46,0:05:24.26,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you, stupid?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.26,0:05:26.55,Default,,0,0,0,,In the end, you're just doing it for yourself!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.51,0:05:30.68,Default,,0,0,0,,And there you go, making up excuses\Nfor yourself again!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.24,0:05:32.83,Default,,0,0,0,,I am?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.83,0:05:36.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Thinking that you're working hard\Nfor the sake of others!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.44,0:05:38.87,Default,,0,0,0,,That in and of itself is the easy way to live!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.87,0:05:40.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.62,0:05:43.66,Default,,0,0,0,,In other words, you're lonely, Shinji.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.66,0:05:45.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.18,0:05:47.25,Default,,0,0,0,,That's just being dependent!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.25,0:05:49.73,Default,,0,0,0,,It's nothing but a symbiotic relationship!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.73,0:05:51.60,Default,,0,0,0,,You might be right.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.60,0:05:56.16,Default,,0,0,0,,You just want people to need you!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.50,0:05:58.46,Default,,0,0,0,,You might be right.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.46,0:06:03.40,Default,,0,0,0,,All you do is wait, wanting people\Nto give you happiness!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.40,0:06:05.14,Default,,0,0,0,,False happiness!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.48,0:06:07.55,Default,,0,0,0,,But that goes for you too.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.26,0:06:09.34,Matisse Sign,,0,0,0,,THE SECOND CHARACTER
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.38,0:06:11.68,Matisse Sign,,0,0,0,,IN THE CASE OF ASUKA LANGLEY SOHRYU
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.02,0:06:19.95,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't remember getting on,\Nbut I'm back in the Eva again.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.95,0:06:21.69,Default,,0,0,0,,I was put back in.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.16,0:06:25.50,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not going to move anyway, piece of junk.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.20,0:06:30.14,Default,,0,0,0,,No, I'm the piece of junk.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.60,0:06:34.90,Default,,0,0,0,,They don't need me! No one needs me!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.77,0:06:39.88,Default,,0,0,0,,No one needs a pilot who can't control her Eva!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.61,0:06:43.37,Default,,0,0,0,,So, you're seeking to find yourself in others.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.37,0:06:44.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.21,0:06:45.09,Matisse Sign,,0,0,0,,SEPARATION ANXIETY
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.68,0:06:47.63,Default,,0,0,0,,You're afraid of becoming alone, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.67,0:06:48.34,Matisse Sign,,0,0,0,,SEPARATION ANXIETY
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.82,0:06:52.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Because you disappear along with the people\Naround you. That's why you're afraid, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.34,0:06:52.84,Matisse Sign,,0,0,0,,SEPARATION ANXIETY
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.09,0:06:55.20,Default,,0,0,0,,That's why you pilot the Eva!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.22,0:06:55.72,Matisse Sign,,0,0,0,,ATTACHMENT BEHAVIOR
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.72,0:06:58.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Shut up! Shut up! Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.60,0:06:57.35,Matisse Sign,,0,0,0,,ATTACHMENT BEHAVIOR
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.80,0:07:01.94,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't want to hear that from a puppet like you!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.98,0:07:03.02,Matisse Sign,,0,0,0,,THE THIRD CHARACTER
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.06,0:07:04.61,Matisse Sign,,0,0,0,,IN THE CASE OF REI AYANAMI
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.20,0:07:06.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Who am I?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.79,0:07:08.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Rei Ayanami.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.49,0:07:10.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Who are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.11,0:07:11.57,Matisse Sign,,0,0,0,,REI AYANAMI
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.94,0:07:14.08,Default,,0,0,0,,You're also Rei Ayanami?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.08,0:07:17.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, I am the thing that is called Rei Ayanami.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.55,0:07:20.46,Default,,0,0,0,,We are all things that are called Rei Ayanami.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.95,0:07:22.92,Default,,0,0,0,,How can we all be me?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.59,0:07:27.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Because everybody calls us Rei Ayanami.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.86,0:07:31.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Why do you possess a false heart and body?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.13,0:07:35.35,Default,,0,0,0,,They are not false, because I am me.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.90,0:07:42.51,Default,,0,0,0,,No, you are a person whose false soul was\Ncreated by the human named Gendo Ikari.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.24,0:07:47.61,Default,,0,0,0,,You're nothing but an object living a lie,\Npretending to be a person.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.01,0:07:50.84,Default,,0,0,0,,See? There's a dark part\Nof your heart inside you
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.84,0:07:54.53,Default,,0,0,0,,that you can see nothing of,\Nthat you know nothing of.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.15,0:07:57.96,Default,,0,0,0,,That's where the real you is.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.96,0:07:59.86,Default,,0,0,0,,I am me.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.86,0:08:02.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Because I became who I am\Nthrough the time I've spent
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.85,0:08:05.29,Default,,0,0,0,,and the connections I've made\Nwith other people.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.16,0:08:11.04,Default,,0,0,0,,The current me has been molded\Nthrough contact with other people.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.04,0:08:16.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Contact with people and the passage of time\Nchange the shape of my heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.22,0:08:17.43,Matisse Sign,,0,0,0,,"IS THAT WHAT TIES ARE?"
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.64,0:08:22.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, the things that have created the me\Ncalled Rei Ayanami so far...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.38,0:08:25.46,Default,,0,0,0,,The things that will continue to shape me...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.48,0:08:26.77,Matisse Sign,,0,0,0,,"THAT IS WHAT TIES ARE"
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.12,0:08:30.03,Default,,0,0,0,,But the real you is somewhere else.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.99,0:08:32.99,Default,,0,0,0,,You just don't know it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.03,0:08:35.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Because you don't want to see it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.68,0:08:37.70,Default,,0,0,0,,You're just avoiding it without realizing it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.74,0:08:38.83,Matisse Sign,,0,0,0,,"BECAUSE YOU'RE AFRAID"
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.87,0:08:41.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Because it may not be human in form.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.63,0:08:45.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Because the person that I have been\Nso far may cease to exist.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.42,0:08:47.58,Matisse Sign,,0,0,0,,"YOU ARE AFRAID"
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.58,0:08:50.38,Default,,0,0,0,,You're afraid of ceasing to exist.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.94,0:08:54.88,Default,,0,0,0,,You're afraid of being erased\Nfrom everyone's hearts.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.88,0:08:56.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Afraid?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.44,0:08:57.74,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.74,0:09:00.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Your own individual world\Nwill also cease to exist.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.43,0:09:01.52,Matisse Sign,,0,0,0,,"IT FRIGHTENS YOU, DOESN'T IT?"
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.52,0:09:03.39,Default,,0,0,0,,You will cease to exist.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.43,0:09:04.52,Matisse Sign,,0,0,0,,"IT FRIGHTENS YOU, DOESN'T IT?"
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.89,0:09:08.07,Default,,0,0,0,,No, it makes me happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.63,0:09:10.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Because I want to die.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.82,0:09:12.65,Default,,0,0,0,,What I desire is despair.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.65,0:09:14.29,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to return to nothingness.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.29,0:09:15.79,Default,,0,0,0,,But I can't.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.79,0:09:17.69,Default,,0,0,0,,I cannot return to nothingness.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.69,0:09:19.47,Default,,0,0,0,,He won't let me return.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.21,0:09:22.14,Default,,0,0,0,,He won't let me go back yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.57,0:09:25.12,Default,,0,0,0,,I existed because he needed me.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.51,0:09:27.30,Default,,0,0,0,,But it's over now.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.30,0:09:29.50,Default,,0,0,0,,He's not going to need me anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.50,0:09:31.89,Default,,0,0,0,,He's going to abandon me.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.59,0:09:35.33,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought I had wished for\Nthat day to come, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.12,0:09:38.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, I am afraid.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.43,0:09:44.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Come, let us go.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.43,0:09:49.10,Default,,0,0,0,,You have existed for this day, today, Rei.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.67,0:09:50.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.40,0:09:51.44,Matisse Sign,,0,0,0,,AND THEN...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.48,0:09:53.44,Matisse Sign,,0,0,0,,THE INSTRUMENTALITY OF MANKIND BEGINS
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.48,0:09:55.86,Title Cards,,0,0,0,,{\fs70\pos(773,385)}EPISODE 25
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.48,0:09:55.86,Title Cards,,0,0,0,,{\fs100\pos(500,797)}THE WORLD ENDING
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.78,0:09:59.99,Matisse Sign,,0,0,0,,ONCE AGAIN, SHINJI IKARI
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.78,0:10:03.99,Default,,0,0,0,,What is this sensation?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.62,0:10:07.14,Default,,0,0,0,,I feel like I've experienced it before,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.14,0:10:10.16,Default,,0,0,0,,as if the shape of my body is melting away.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.09,0:10:12.89,Default,,0,0,0,,It feels so good.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.73,0:10:16.66,Default,,0,0,0,,I feel like I'm growing, expanding outward...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.13,0:10:19.80,Default,,0,0,0,,On and on...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.18,0:10:21.80,Matisse Sign,,0,0,0,,THAT WAS THE BEGINNING OF THE\NINSTRUMENTALITY OF PEOPLE
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.85,0:10:23.05,Matisse Sign,,0,0,0,,WHAT PEOPLE ARE LACKING
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.10,0:10:24.26,Matisse Sign,,0,0,0,,THE LOSS IN THEIR HEARTS
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.31,0:10:25.60,Matisse Sign,,0,0,0,,IN ORDER TO FILL THAT VOID IN THEIR HEARTS
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.64,0:10:27.60,Matisse Sign,,0,0,0,,THE INSTRUMENTALITY OF HEARTS\NAND SOULS BEGINS
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.64,0:10:28.85,Matisse Sign,,0,0,0,,RETURNING ALL THINGS TO NOTHINGNESS
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.89,0:10:31.02,Matisse Sign,,0,0,0,,THE INSTRUMENTALITY OF PEOPLE HAD BEGUN
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.18,0:10:35.20,Default,,0,0,0,,No, it is not that we are returning\Nto nothingness.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.20,0:10:38.04,Default,,0,0,0,,We are only restoring everything\Nto its original state.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.04,0:10:41.49,Default,,0,0,0,,We are only returning to our mother,\Nwho has been lost to this world.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.49,0:10:45.32,Default,,0,0,0,,All souls will become one\Nand find eternal peace.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.72,0:10:48.21,Default,,0,0,0,,That is all there is to it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.21,0:10:49.75,Default,,0,0,0,,And that's the Instrumentality Project?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.75,0:10:50.88,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.88,0:10:55.44,Default,,0,0,0,,There is always a void, a part that\Nhas been lost in our hearts.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.55,0:10:56.76,Matisse Sign,,0,0,0,,THAT IS WHAT GIVES RISE TO THE\NHUNGER IN OUR HEARTS
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.80,0:10:58.38,Matisse Sign,,0,0,0,,THIS IS WHAT GIVES RISE TO FEAR AND INSECURITY
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.94,0:11:01.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Every single person fears that\Ndarkness in their heart
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.66,0:11:05.34,Default,,0,0,0,,and lives life trying to escape from it,\Nto banish it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.34,0:11:08.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Even though it will never disappear\Nas long as we remain human.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.67,0:11:11.40,Default,,0,0,0,,That's why you're going to bundle\Nall human souls together,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.40,0:11:13.67,Default,,0,0,0,,so we can compensate for\Nthe void in each other?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.67,0:11:16.71,Default,,0,0,0,,And you're just going to do this to everyone?!\NMind your own business!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.71,0:11:19.24,Default,,0,0,0,,That's nothing more than\Na conspiracy to deceive us!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.24,0:11:21.66,Default,,0,0,0,,But you've been wishing for it to happen too.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.93,0:11:25.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Where am I?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.78,0:11:27.24,Matisse Sign,,0,0,0,,IN THE CASE OF MISATO KATSURAGI
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.83,0:11:31.69,Default,,0,0,0,,This is the me that exists\Nin your mind, Miss Misato.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.69,0:11:35.88,Default,,0,0,0,,And at the same time, the me\Nthat exists in your mind, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.21,0:11:40.61,Default,,0,0,0,,I must connect with all sorts of people\Nin order for me to find who I am.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.08,0:11:43.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I must search deep within myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.88,0:11:46.64,Default,,0,0,0,,I must search deep within the Miss Misato\Nthat exists in my mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.49,0:11:49.52,Default,,0,0,0,,What is it that you want, Miss Misato?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.56,0:11:50.73,Matisse Sign,,0,0,0,,"YOU WANT TO BE A GOOD GIRL?"
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.73,0:11:53.14,Default,,0,0,0,,I have to be a good girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.19,0:11:54.15,Matisse Sign,,0,0,0,,"WHY?"
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.15,0:11:55.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Because my dad's not around.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.75,0:11:59.42,Default,,0,0,0,,I have to help my mom and be a good girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.42,0:12:01.95,Default,,0,0,0,,But I don't want to become like my mom,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.95,0:12:05.49,Default,,0,0,0,,because she's always crying\Nwhen my dad isn't here.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.49,0:12:08.08,Default,,0,0,0,,No crying, no being spoiled.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.28,0:12:11.36,Default,,0,0,0,,That's why I have to be a good girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.36,0:12:14.61,Default,,0,0,0,,And I'm going to do my best\Nso my dad won't hate me.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.61,0:12:16.80,Default,,0,0,0,,But I hate my father.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.80,0:12:18.94,Default,,0,0,0,,That's why I hate being good too.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.94,0:12:20.81,Default,,0,0,0,,I hate it all now.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.81,0:12:22.44,Default,,0,0,0,,And I'm so tired.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.44,0:12:24.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Of having to maintain my clean image.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.94,0:12:27.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Of myself, for keeping up this pretense\Nof being so pristine.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.76,0:12:29.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm just tired of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.16,0:12:32.46,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to be dirty.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.46,0:12:35.29,Default,,0,0,0,,I wanted to see what I looked like\Nwhen I was no longer perfect.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.29,0:12:37.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that why you slept with him? With that man?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.69,0:12:41.04,Default,,0,0,0,,No, I slept with him because I loved him.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.94,0:12:44.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you really love him?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.03,0:12:45.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, I did.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.36,0:12:47.92,Default,,0,0,0,,He accepted me for who I am.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.95,0:12:48.74,Matisse Sign,,0,0,0,,"REALLY?"
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.01,0:12:50.24,Default,,0,0,0,,He was kind to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.67,0:13:06.59,Default,,0,0,0,,No! Stop it! Don't show this part of me to Shinji!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.93,0:13:10.56,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no reason to be embarrassed\Nafter all that has happened.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.56,0:13:12.39,Default,,0,0,0,,It IS embarrassing!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.39,0:13:14.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Why is it embarrassing?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.09,0:13:17.63,Default,,0,0,0,,You have no problem...\Nno, you actually enjoy
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.63,0:13:19.77,Default,,0,0,0,,presenting this side of yourself\Nto the man you love.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.77,0:13:21.19,Default,,0,0,0,,No! Please stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.78,0:13:27.01,Default,,0,0,0,,In all honesty, you are actually\Nhappy to show this to Shinji.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.01,0:13:29.54,Default,,0,0,0,,That's a lie! You're wrong! Wrong!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.54,0:13:31.01,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.01,0:13:33.78,Default,,0,0,0,,You actually want to show this\Nto your father, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.78,0:13:35.18,Default,,0,0,0,,You're wrong!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.18,0:13:38.88,Default,,0,0,0,,You sought peace in Kaji's face as he slept.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.88,0:13:39.82,Default,,0,0,0,,You're wrong!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.82,0:13:42.99,Default,,0,0,0,,You sought peace in Kaji's warmth.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.99,0:13:44.39,Default,,0,0,0,,You're wrong!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.39,0:13:47.88,Default,,0,0,0,,You sought your father in Kaji's arms.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.88,0:13:48.89,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not true!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.08,0:13:52.80,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.80,0:13:57.25,Default,,0,0,0,,That time, I saw my own father in Kaji.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.78,0:14:00.29,Default,,0,0,0,,That's why I ran away from him.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.62,0:14:03.31,Default,,0,0,0,,I was scared.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.31,0:14:05.49,Default,,0,0,0,,It was as if he were my father and...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.99,0:14:08.65,Default,,0,0,0,,But it was actually because I was happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.65,0:14:10.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I derived pleasure from it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.80,0:14:13.85,Default,,0,0,0,,It was a moment of unbearably\Nwonderful feeling.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.85,0:14:15.95,Default,,0,0,0,,That's why I hated it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.95,0:14:18.06,Default,,0,0,0,,That's why I split up with him.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.06,0:14:21.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I guess it just means love\Nbegins for no reason,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.83,0:14:24.01,Default,,0,0,0,,but always ends for a reason.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.14,0:14:27.37,Default,,0,0,0,,You're so kind, Kaji.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.15,0:14:31.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Please take that kindness...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.72,0:14:34.51,Default,,0,0,0,,...and tarnish me with it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.49,0:14:39.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Just because you hate yourself now
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.01,0:14:41.05,Default,,0,0,0,,doesn't mean you should hurt yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.05,0:14:46.23,Default,,0,0,0,,That's just fooling yourself into feeling better\Nby punishing yourself for the moment.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.46,0:14:48.49,Default,,0,0,0,,You should stop doing that.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.49,0:14:52.29,Default,,0,0,0,,And you're going to tell me\Nto be good to myself, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.29,0:14:54.13,Default,,0,0,0,,That's what all men are like.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.13,0:14:58.38,Default,,0,0,0,,And after that, they go off to work,\Ninto their own worlds.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.38,0:15:00.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Leaving me behind...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.41,0:15:03.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Just like Father.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.08,0:15:07.22,Default,,0,0,0,,All I'm ever doing is running away\Nfrom the harsh reality.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.22,0:15:09.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Harsh reality?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.17,0:15:10.94,Default,,0,0,0,,That's me, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.94,0:15:14.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course, just look at me.\NIt's only to be expected.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.23,0:15:18.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop it, Miss Misato!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.93,0:15:22.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Sometimes, I lose all hope for myself!\NI hate it!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.44,0:15:24.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Filth, you're so dirty.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.92,0:15:26.02,Default,,0,0,0,,You're pathetic.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.02,0:15:28.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Disgusting! You're just foul!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.23,0:15:31.07,Default,,0,0,0,,That's what you call a mature relationship?!\NYou make me puke!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.41,0:15:35.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Congratulations on your promotion,\NMajor Katsuragi.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.37,0:15:36.97,Default,,0,0,0,,The person being recognized
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.97,0:15:39.64,Default,,0,0,0,,is the me who's putting on a performance\Nin order to be recognized.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.64,0:15:41.29,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not the real me.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.02,0:15:45.11,Default,,0,0,0,,The real you is always crying.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.11,0:15:47.73,Default,,0,0,0,,No, I'm happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.75,0:15:48.67,Matisse Sign,,0,0,0,,"AM I HAPPY?"
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.89,0:15:50.87,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.88,0:15:51.84,Matisse Sign,,0,0,0,,"AM I HAPPY?"
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.84,0:15:53.68,Default,,0,0,0,,I am happy!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.72,0:15:54.68,Matisse Sign,,0,0,0,,"AM I HAPPY?"
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.83,0:15:57.44,Default,,0,0,0,,No! This isn't happiness!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.47,0:15:58.43,Matisse Sign,,0,0,0,,"WHAT IS HAPPINESS?"
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.43,0:16:01.39,Default,,0,0,0,,This isn't the real me!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.39,0:16:03.66,Default,,0,0,0,,I've only made myself believe that it is!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.66,0:16:06.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that what we have to do to keep on living?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.25,0:16:09.37,Default,,0,0,0,,You're afraid when you're not together.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.37,0:16:10.77,Default,,0,0,0,,You're insecure.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.77,0:16:12.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Unless someone's sleeping by your side.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.94,0:16:15.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you scared of sleeping by yourself?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.17,0:16:18.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you lonely sleeping by yourself after all?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.01,0:16:20.43,Default,,0,0,0,,You can't bear the loss in your heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.06,0:16:22.96,Default,,0,0,0,,That's why you'll be with anyone,\Nit doesn't matter who.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.96,0:16:24.52,Default,,0,0,0,,That's not true!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.52,0:16:28.19,Default,,0,0,0,,No, you just want to give yourself\Nover to simple pleasure.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.19,0:16:31.49,Default,,0,0,0,,You just want to soothe your soul\Nthrough temporary escapes
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.49,0:16:34.43,Default,,0,0,0,,and you're only using men to that end.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.43,0:16:36.58,Default,,0,0,0,,No! You're wrong! Wrong!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.68,0:16:40.31,Matisse Sign,,0,0,0,,WHAT COULD IT BE THAT SHE WANTS?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.85,0:16:43.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Where am I?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.85,0:16:47.71,Default,,0,0,0,,This is the me that exists in your mind, Asuka.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.71,0:16:51.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Which means, it's also the me\Nthat exists in your mind, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.44,0:16:53.90,Matisse Sign,,0,0,0,,IN THE CASE OF ASUKA LANGLEY SOHRYU
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.39,0:16:56.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Asuka, what do you want?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.16,0:16:59.42,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm going to live on my own!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.42,0:17:02.55,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't need Mom or Dad.\NI'm going to live by myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.55,0:17:04.64,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not going to cry anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.17,0:17:08.21,Default,,0,0,0,,But I'm still crying...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.61,0:17:10.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Why am I crying?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.08,0:17:14.60,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know how to deal with that child.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.60,0:17:17.64,Default,,0,0,0,,What's this? You, a doctor, getting\Ndiscouraged? It isn't like you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.64,0:17:19.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Even doctors are human,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.44,0:17:21.22,Default,,0,0,0,,as I have mentioned before.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.52,0:17:25.51,Default,,0,0,0,,But a woman like you having\Ntrouble with a child...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.51,0:17:27.28,Default,,0,0,0,,She's oddly mature,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.28,0:17:30.42,Default,,0,0,0,,and there's a sense of vigilant\Nand absolute rejection.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.42,0:17:32.58,Default,,0,0,0,,It scares me sometimes.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.58,0:17:35.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Haven't you ever felt that way, dear?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.25,0:17:36.72,Default,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.72,0:17:40.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Anyway, you're Asuka's mother now.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.02,0:17:43.86,Default,,0,0,0,,But before that, I first became your wife.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.86,0:17:45.10,Default,,0,0,0,,You became both at the same time.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.10,0:17:48.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, from a social standpoint, that's true.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.58,0:17:51.84,Default,,0,0,0,,But you can never stop being that child's father,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.84,0:17:55.65,Default,,0,0,0,,whereas I can quit being her mother at any time.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.65,0:17:57.34,Default,,0,0,0,,True enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.34,0:18:00.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't, Mom! Don't quit being my mom!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.41,0:18:03.18,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll be a good girl, so you'll like me!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.18,0:18:05.39,Default,,0,0,0,,So, don't quit being my mom!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.39,0:18:07.42,Default,,0,0,0,,So, look at me!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.42,0:18:08.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop, Mom!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.65,0:18:10.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't kill me!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.11,0:18:15.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Your dad doesn't love your mom anymore.\NHe doesn't need me.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.14,0:18:19.32,Default,,0,0,0,,No, he never loved me to begin with.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.64,0:18:22.55,Default,,0,0,0,,He probably didn't need me from the start.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.85,0:18:28.04,Default,,0,0,0,,So, die with me, because your dad\Ndoesn't need us.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.04,0:18:30.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Am I a bother? Am I not needed?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.33,0:18:33.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Please die with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.67,0:18:37.16,Default,,0,0,0,,No! I'm not your doll, Mom!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.16,0:18:39.72,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll think for myself and live on my own!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.87,0:18:45.23,Default,,0,0,0,,That time, my mom was hanging\Nfrom the ceiling.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.24,0:18:49.10,Default,,0,0,0,,The expression on her face\Nlooked very happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.64,0:18:53.48,Default,,0,0,0,,But I hated that look on her face.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.08,0:18:58.15,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't want to die. I don't want to disappear.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.15,0:19:01.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I hate boys. I hate Mom and Dad too!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.19,0:19:03.98,Default,,0,0,0,,I hate everybody!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.98,0:19:06.82,Default,,0,0,0,,No one will protect me.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.82,0:19:08.87,Default,,0,0,0,,No one will stay with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.91,0:19:10.37,Matisse Sign,,0,0,0,,WHAT DOES SHE WANT?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.13,0:19:13.50,Default,,0,0,0,,That's why I'm going to live by myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.50,0:19:16.07,Default,,0,0,0,,But I don't want to! It's hard!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.53,0:19:18.29,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't want to be alone!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.29,0:19:20.14,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't want to be alone!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.14,0:19:22.47,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't want to be alone!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.18,0:19:27.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't forsake me.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.00,0:19:28.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't abandon me.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.47,0:19:30.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't kill me.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.65,0:19:33.86,Default,,0,0,0,,What is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.09,0:19:40.41,Default,,0,0,0,,The Human Instrumentality Project\Nthat your father was working on.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.41,0:19:41.41,Default,,0,0,0,,This is?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.41,0:19:43.25,Default,,0,0,0,,It appears to be part of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.25,0:19:46.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Because the truth eludes even us.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.50,0:19:51.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Only what you can feel for yourself\Nright now is fact.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.57,0:19:53.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Within you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.54,0:19:57.80,Default,,0,0,0,,And your memory of those things\Nwill become the truth for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.18,0:20:01.33,Default,,0,0,0,,There are also some truths\Nthat change with time.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.33,0:20:05.30,Default,,0,0,0,,So, this is fact, the result of everything\Nthat was done. This...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.30,0:20:08.32,Default,,0,0,0,,There are a lot of realities.\NThis is one of them.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.69,0:20:10.81,Default,,0,0,0,,This is the result you wished for.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.36,0:20:13.08,Default,,0,0,0,,The one I wished for?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.08,0:20:17.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, annihilation, a world\Nwhere no one is saved.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.35,0:20:21.40,Default,,0,0,0,,No! It's just that no one saved me! No one...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.90,0:20:23.82,Default,,0,0,0,,No one can save you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.82,0:20:26.57,Default,,0,0,0,,This is what you wished for.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.57,0:20:29.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Destruction, death, the return to nothingness...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.96,0:20:32.16,Default,,0,0,0,,It's what you wished for.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.16,0:20:34.07,Default,,0,0,0,,This is reality.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.07,0:20:35.93,Default,,0,0,0,,What is reality?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.93,0:20:37.90,Default,,0,0,0,,It's your world.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.90,0:20:42.09,Default,,0,0,0,,It's your own world where you coexist\Nwith time, space, and other people.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.49,0:20:47.35,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a world where you yourself decide\Nhow to perceive and accept it.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.35,0:20:50.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Right now, this is your world,\Nwhere everything is given to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.72,0:20:51.85,Matisse Sign,,0,0,0,,THAT IS REALITY
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.26,0:20:54.60,Default,,0,0,0,,This is your world, which cannot be helped.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.10,0:20:58.12,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a world where everything's already set!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.12,0:21:01.34,Default,,0,0,0,,You're wrong. It's a world where\Nyou make the decisions.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.34,0:21:04.95,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a world where your heart\Nhas decided that it is so.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.99,0:21:06.11,Matisse Sign,,0,0,0,,THIS IS REALITY
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.11,0:21:07.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Your will to live...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.95,0:21:11.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Your thoughts of wanting to die...\NThey are all what you wished for.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.95,0:21:15.04,Default,,0,0,0,,You're saying even this darkness\Nand this world of half measures
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.04,0:21:17.28,Default,,0,0,0,,are all things I wished for?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.28,0:21:18.44,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.44,0:21:22.76,Default,,0,0,0,,You wished for a closed world,\Nwhere you alone are comfortable.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.76,0:21:25.65,Default,,0,0,0,,In order to protect the weakness of your heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.65,0:21:28.25,Default,,0,0,0,,In order to protect your pleasures in life.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.25,0:21:30.43,Default,,0,0,0,,This is merely the result.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.43,0:21:32.89,Default,,0,0,0,,For people cannot live in a world\Nthat is yours alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.89,0:21:35.53,Default,,0,0,0,,They cannot live in a space\Nthat is closed off.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.53,0:21:40.20,Default,,0,0,0,,But you wished for the world, the world\Nthat surrounds you, to be closed off.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.20,0:21:43.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Your heart and mind eliminated\Neverything you didn't like
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.87,0:21:45.74,Default,,0,0,0,,and wished for a world as solitary as possible.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.74,0:21:49.92,Default,,0,0,0,,And that has led to this little haven for your soul.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.24,0:21:54.88,Default,,0,0,0,,This is one of the many ends that could occur.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.88,0:21:58.40,Default,,0,0,0,,This is the end of the world\Nthat you have brought about.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.42,0:21:59.96,Matisse Sign,,0,0,0,,AND THE JOURNEY TOWARDS INSTRUMENTALITY...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.00,0:22:01.63,Matisse Sign,,0,0,0,,...WILL CONTINUE
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.07,0:23:07.90,Preview Card,,0,0,0,,PREVIEW
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.90,0:23:11.69,Default,,0,0,0,,The end, it is something that always\Ncomes after the beginning.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.69,0:23:14.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Will our wishes lead to destruction?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.26,0:23:16.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Is our hope death itself?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.86,0:23:20.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Final episode: "The Beast That Shouted Love\Nat the Heart of the World"
